
'''= TinyLightbulbs is a dedicated marketplace for products that have been launched through crowdfunding, aiming to help startups after funding has been secured.''' 

URL = http://www.tinylightbulbs.com/


=Description=

"While sites such as Kickstarter provide a popular platform for small startups to get their ideas heard about and funded, the group behind TinyLightbulbs suggests that once those startups reach their target, they no longer have the backing of a frequently visited site to support and market their products. Acting as a marketplace for those independent businesses that have completed their fundraising drives, the website aims to promote new products, sell them, and offer advice to small businesses. The site features video reviews of new merchandise and is hoping to build a community for startups."
(http://www.springwise.com/retail/dedicated-marketplace-crowd-funded-goods)


